              class="pt-1 pl-1 pr-1 font-medium text-primary-300 transition duration-250
              hover:text-snow-100 hover:bg-primary-100 "
            >NTT DATA.</a>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 lg:mt-8 w-fit">
